name: Wintertime Snow Art Frame
description:
These photo frames are handmade by me. I take an ordinary wood frame and create a one of a kind artwork to surround your photo. I use a multitude of mixed media including but not limited to paper, chipboard, paint, polymer clay, stamping, glitter, fabric, beads and more. 

Each frame goes through a creation process in which I may need to create special clay pieces and fire them. Chipboard gets painted, stamped and glittered. Each piece ends up special and no two are alike. 

Each frame arrives wrapped in tissue paper with a bow; Perfect for gift giving. 

Materials included in this frame include:
wood, paper, paint, glitter, ink, crackle medium, fabric

This frame measures 12"x 12" with a 5"x 7" photo insert.
